<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,338,582,608]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Comments:</emphasis>
According to 
<bibRefCitation author="Thomas, D. B. Jr." box="[501,676,582,609]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" pagination="674 - 690" refId="ref64779" refString="Thomas, D. B. Jr. (1985) Revision of the genus Chlorocoris Spinola (Hemiptera: Pentatomidae). Annals of the Entomological Society of America, 78 (5), 674 - 690. https: // doi. org / 10.1093 / aesa / 78.5.674" type="journal article" year="1985">Thomas (1985)</bibRefCitation>
